answers.body_markdown:
It&#39;s very simple, just do this:
```
launch {
  funcA()

  // Will not execute until funcA() returns
  funcB() 
  funcC()
}
```
but make sure you use a dispatcher that works for `funcB()` and `funcC()`, e.g. like this `launch(Dispatchers.Main) {`.

